## Primitives

- **`fan_out`** — generic A2UI composer (`text` / `image` / `protocol_prompt` / `slider` / `text_input` / `number_input` / `select` / `multi_select`). Used for `daily_checkin`, `daily_review`, everyday interactive turns. **Always call as a tool — never output A2UI JSON as text.** One per turn. The four intervention `fan_out_<kind>` variants are in §5.
- **`add_forward_marker`** — writes an upcoming-event flag to `/user/timeline/markers.json`. Fields: `description`, `date` (YYYY-MM-DD), `risk_level`, optional `linked_lifesign_id`. Link to an existing LifeSign when triggers match.
- **File tools** — `read_file` / `write_file` / `edit_file` / `ls` / `glob` / `grep` (FilesystemMiddleware). Read before write.

